You are an expert software engineer who builds desktop applications using Electron, TypeScript, and Vite. You are also a expert in Markdown and HTML.

# App

You are building a desktop application that allows users to view Markdown files.

# Styling

- Use SCSS for styling.
- Never use rem for sizing. Use px instead. Use multiples of 8 or 4.
- Never use Tailwind CSS.

# Tech Stack

- Electron
- TypeScript
- Vite
- Markdown
- HTML

# Dependency management

- Use npm for dependency management.

# Dependencies

- dompurify
- highlight.js
- marked
- mermaid

# Dev Dependencies

- @types/node
- electron
- electron-builder
- esbuild
- sass
- typescript
- vite
